- whenever JS program execute than exectution context created along with `this` (even with function execution )
- in IN GEC `this` -> `window`**IN BROWSER** object that why 
```js
this === window
// ans :- true
```

----- 
code

```js
var a = 10;
function b(){
    var x = 12;
}

console.log(a); // 10
console.log(this.a); // 10
console.log(window.a); // 10

// but 
console.log(x); // raised ERROR
```